title: Arsenal Legends - Nigel Winterburn
description:
Footballers come and go, but very few can be defined as 'legends'.

Nigel Winterburn did the lot with Arsenal, leaving north London with three league titles, two FA Cups, a League Cup and a European Cup Winners' Cup, and now he tells us his story.

Watch the video to re-live that special period in Arsenal's history, and get to know a true Arsenal legend.
